s be upon him, said, \u201cNone of you greets me with peace (at his grave) except Allah returns my spirit, that I may return his greeting of peace.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2041 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8141,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/14\/preferred-tashahhud-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":36873,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: Variants of Prayer&#8217;s ending supplication","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would teach us the testimony of faith in prayer, just as he would teach us a chapter from the Quran. The Prophet would say, \u201cGreetings, blessings, prayers, and good words are for Allah. Peace be upon you,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33923,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/13\/istighfar-after-salah\/","url_meta":{"origin":36873,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Seeking forgiveness, supplicating after prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 13, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: When the Messenger of Allah peace and blessings be upon him, finished his prayer, he would seek forgiveness from Allah three times and he would say, \u201cO Allah, You are peace and from You is peace. Blessed are You, Majestic and Generous.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 591 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37549,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/16\/salaam-bani-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":36873,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ziyarah: Peace be on the Prophet, Abu Bakr, and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Nafi\u2019 reported: Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, when he arrived on his journey, he would enter the mosque of Medina and then go to the graves. Ibn Umar would say, \u201cPeace be upon you, O Messenger of Allah. Peace be upon you, O Abu Bakr. Peace be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":738,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/04\/28\/o-allah-you-are-peace\/","url_meta":{"origin":36873,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Peace: O Allah, you are peace and from you is peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, finished his prayer, he would not sit long enough but to say,\u00a0\u201cO Allah, You are peace and from You is peace. Blessed are You, the Majestic and Noble.\u2